The paper discusses the propagation of memes in scientific literature, which involves analyzing citation networks. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories in computer science, including social networks (cs.SI), digital libraries (cs.DL), scientometrics (cs.SD), information retrieval (cs.IR), and computational sociology (cs.CY).
